com.xceptance.xlt.common.util.action.data

Class CSVBasedURLActionDataListBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.xceptance.xlt.common.util.action.data.URLActionDataListBuilder
      • com.xceptance.xlt.common.util.action.data.CSVBasedURLActionDataListBuilder

  • public class CSVBasedURLActionDataListBuilder
extends URLActionDataListBuilder
    Implementation of the URLActionDataListBuilder for files of type 'CSV'.
    • Takes a file of type csv and build a List<#URLActionData> from it.
    • The structure of the data is determined within this class and described in syntax.csv
    • The names of the tags, whose values should be parsed into a URLActionData are also determined here.
    • If you want to change the names of the tags, you can do it easily.
    Author:
    matthias mitterreiter
